name: A Fund Baby
description: A Fund Baby (AFB) is a project that exist to spread the great narrative of Teh Fund. AFB has two products online. The first is a Twitter A.I. bot in the form of a boy named ELON. ELON is very wise compared to how he looks. The second product is a Dapp known as Bitcoin Seekers. This Dapp automatically allows AFB holders to search for wallets that may have lost bitcoin in it. The project continues to develop other features that the community decides. The dev of the project is mysterious yet generous and he only communicates through the blockchain.
